::Prowl::

Carrying Zenyak through the forest, Prowl wonders if he had offended Iron 
Raptor by refusing her offer. He shrugs. If he did, he could always apologise 
later.

Suddenly, Prowl's thoughts are interupted by a sharp and severe pain in his 
right shoulder. Zenyak growls and stabs his dagger again near the first hole 
his dagger had made.

Swearing under his breath, Prowl throws Zenyak into a tree. The predacon hits 
the tree and falls to the ground, unconscious again.

Prowl growls and reaches behind him to pull Zenyak's dagger out of his 
shoulder. Mechfluid flows freely from the wound. Putting the dagger away in a 
storage compartment, Prowl turns to Iron Raptor.

"I think I should fly him back to base so he doesn't try anything else. Think 
you can keep up?"
